  <brief_title>Efficacy of Transdermal Fentanyl Patches in Relief of Acute Postoperative Pain After Mastectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Transdermal Fentanyl Patches in Relief of Acute Postoperative Pain After Mastectomy</official_title>
