  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  ASA I - II patients

          -  aged 30-60 years

          -  body weight ranged between 65-10kg

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with history of allergy to morphine

          -  chronic intake of analgesics or non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drug 24 h prior to
             surgery,

          -  there was a history of a psychiatric disorder patients weight was less then 50kg.

          -  impaired kidney function.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
